1097
01:17:49,757 --> 01:17:50,906
l've been asked, yes.

1098
01:17:53,717 --> 01:17:55,309
l guess that means...

1099
01:17:55,917 --> 01:17:58,636
...that you're a selector,
l'm a selectee and we can't...

1100
